Inputs -> system -> output

{% raw %} 
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(10, 5))

box = Box(3, 5, 3, 2, 'system')
box.fontcolor = 'darkred'
box.fontsize = 27
box.draw()

arrow = Arrow(1, 5, 2.6, 5)
arrow._head_width=0.3
arrow.draw()

arrow = Arrow(4.1, 5, 6.5, 5)
arrow._head_width=0.3
arrow.draw()

plt.text(1, 5.8, 'inputs', color='darkred')
plt.text(5.2, 5.8, 'outputs', color='darkred')


plt.xlim(0, 8)
plt.ylim(0, 10)

bm = BlockManager()
bm.clean_plot()
bm.save_plot('img/4.system-1.png')
